title: Dispensary
cleaned_text: We carry clean, extensively testing supplements so you know that what the labels says on the bottle is what you are getting in your supplement. We select fish oils that are testing not just once a year but EVERY BATCH is tested for heavy metals, pesticides and free radicals. You are not obligated to purchase any of your supplements from our office we just try to make sure the best is available to you. We hand-select the best products from various companies. Here is a sample of the companies we order from: - Biotics - Bioimmersion - Integrative Therapeutics Maintenance - Metagenics - Pharmax - Researched Nutritionals - Standard Process - Thorne Research - Vital Nutrients
